This search is intended to find high quality images which (as far as possible) are [[public domain]], i.e. without copyright restrictions. A number of galleries are indexed. 

'''INSTRUCTIONS''': Search, then click the Image tab on the results page. Then click a filter to narrow down your search (Smithsonian, Technology, Health, Nature or Agriculture).

'''WARNING''': Please check for copyright notices before using as public domain. The default view contains non-PD images, especially from the Smithsonian. The "Smithsonian" tab shows just images from that site which are tagged as public domain (but we haven't managed to do that for the main view).

== Other options ==

You can also search images on the [[Public Domain Search]] (via the Image tab). Both are useful, but give different results. 

